%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C3%8Dch/Tr%C3%BAc-song-v%C4%83n-phong-k%C3%BD-Mi%C3%AAu-Ph%C3%A1t-T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%B1/poem-a9o70FfLlaUx8kVu4YHKQA">Trúc song văn phong ký Miêu Phát, Tư Không Thự - 竹窗聞風寄苗發司空曙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C3%8Dch/author-WesEXQEj_Uo-QKdZcJ784w">Lý Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0-I/poem-kbcDF_RWSDoJ3P3npmv5CQ">Trường tương tư (I) - 長相思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%C3%B9ng-ca-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Nghi%C3%AAm-nh%E1%BB%8B-bi%E1%BB%87t-gi%C3%A1/poem-5aK2JlX-k3k02Onr4xn2SQ">Tương phùng ca, tặng Nghiêm nhị biệt giá - 相逢歌贈嚴二別駕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
